The incident occurred on the N11 about 25km from Middelburg around 03:30. All the injured passengers were initially transported to the Middelburg Provincial Hospital for medical assistance.  Shortly after 15:00 one of the patients, a woman, was airlifted to the Lenmed Ahmed Kathrada Hospital in Lenasia.
Another patient, a man, was transported by ambulance to the same hospital later that day. The other six passengers are still receiving medical treatment at the Middelburg Provincial Hospital. 